<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
  <% include ./partials/head.ejs %>
</head>

<body>

  <div id="layout">
    <% include ./partials/navbar.ejs %>
      <main class="pure-g">
					<div class="pure-u-1">
						<div class="title-bar-left"></div>
							<section class="home-title">
								<h1>Welcome To Blocipedia</h1>
								<h2>Start Sharing Today!</h2>
								<% include ./partials/messages.ejs %>
								<img src="http://printablegraphics.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Linkedin-background-photo-1024x256.png"/>
								<i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
									<div class="pure-u-1 home-features">
										<p>Welcome to Blocipedia.  An open-source community committed to the sharing of information and ideas from around the world.  Work together to create an open world of ideas and knowledge.  Bridging the gap of information and people</p>
									</div>
							</section>
							<div class="pure-g ">
								<section class="pure-u-1 pure-u-lg-2-3 title-example-main">
									<h2>The beautiful way to wiki.</h2>
									<img src="https://i.imgur.com/MKnPtcn.jpg" alt="wiki page example"/>
								</section>
								<aside class="pure-u-1 pure-u-lg-1-3 features-list">
									<h2>Check Us Out</h2>
									<div class="feature-item">
										<h3>CONNECT</h3>
											<i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
											<p>A premier source for user-generated content.  Connect, share, and learn about any topic.  If you don't find it, add it and share your knowledge with the world.</p>
											<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/users/sign_up">Join Today</a>
									</div>
									<div class="feature-item">
										<h3>COLLABORATE</h3>
											<i class="fas fa-users"></i>
											<p>Work with other members from around the world to have the most complete Wiki possible.  We allow you to edit and have control over content as a Wiki Admin.</p>
											<% if (currentUser) { %>
												<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/users/<%= currentUser.id %>">Premium Content</a>
											<% } else { %>
												<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/users/sign_in">Premium Content</a>
											<% } %>
									</div>
									<div class="feature-item">
										<h3>BEAUTIFY</h3>
											<i class="fas fa-camera-retro"></i>
											<p>Blocipedia is made with design in mind.  Most wiki pages are pretty boring to look at.  But, Blocipedia allows you to share information in a beutiful and dynamic mobile first design.</p>
											<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/wikis">Browse Today</a>
									</div>
									<div class="feature-item">
										<h3>PROTECT</h3>
										<i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
											<p>Premium Users have access to private wikis that only they can see.  You can choose who you would like to share with and who can contribute content as a Premium User.</p>
											<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/users/sign_up">Learn More</a>
									</div>
									<div class="feature-item">
										<h3>LEARN</h3>
										<i class="fas fa-pencil-ruler"></i>
											<p>With users from around the world sharing their knowledge, there is no limit to what you can learn.  From Aa to Zoology, you are free to learn what you want, when you want.  It is only a click away.</p>
											<a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" href="/users/sign_up">Start Exploring</a>
									</div>
								</aside>
							</div>
						</div>
					</main>
			</div>
  </div>
  <% include ./partials/bodyscripts.ejs %>
</body>
